works.description: For audiophiles, the significance of an amplifier holds critical importance, for it determines the quality of sound to be produced from the music systems. This has been shown in our coverage of the Audia Strumento Amplifiers that had ample opportunities for the ultimate musical experiences. Similar to the concept is the GoldAmp A100 amplifier, which magnifies and disperses sound, but is uniquely shaped in the form of a gold bullion to give you a truly ‘golden musical experience’
